One who is in the business of selling information products for profit and using their sales, marketing, writing, editing and proofreading skills. They create products in the areas of newsletters, articles, CD's, books, e-books, podcast and audio products. The Infopreneur also usually does teleseminars and webinars as a form of teaching. They are usually excellent teachers.

Also Infopreneurs are usually experts in the area of research and have the versatility to do work in the areas of a generalist or a niche category.